title: BigFish Games - Adventure Chronicles - The Search for Lost Treas
description:
Adventure Chronicles - The Search for Lost Treasure


After narrowly surviving an earthquake with her daughter 
in Escape the Museum, scientist Susan Anderson decides to 
take advantage of a unique opportunity to travel the world 
while trying to unearth some of the earth's most priceless 
hidden treasures that had been lost to history in Adventure 
Chronicles: The Search For Lost Treasure.


Thanx to TAC-CM
